videos.description: Ivan Bender, Dragan Bender's brother, celebrates Senior Night by getting on a knee and proposing to his girlfriend who says yes.
videos.headline: Maryland senior proposes to girlfriend

videos.description: Anthony Cowan Jr. and Jalen Smith connect on the alley-oop as Smith finishes the play with the dunk.
